com.redhat.rhn.common.db.datasource

Interface ParsedMode


  • public interface ParsedMode
    The DataSourceParserHelper creates an instance of this ParsedQuery for each query it parses. The ParsedQuery is used by ModeFactory when creating new Mode objects and the elaborators and queries contained therein.
